[
    {
        "text": "Hi!",
        "start": 1.41,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m Olivier, welcome to Oxford Online English!",
        "start": 2.41,
        "duration": 4.36
    },
    {
        "text": "When you started learning English, I’m fine\nis probably one of the first things you learnt.",
        "start": 6.77,
        "duration": 6.069
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s a simple way of answering the question\nHow are you?",
        "start": 12.839,
        "duration": 6.031
    },
    {
        "text": "Fine is, well, fine!",
        "start": 18.87,
        "duration": 2.78
    },
    {
        "text": "But if you use it all the time, it can get\nvery repetitive, and a little boring.",
        "start": 21.65,
        "duration": 5.65
    },
    {
        "text": "Does this look familiar to anyone?",
        "start": 27.3,
        "duration": 3.37
    },
    {
        "text": "Hi, how are you?",
        "start": 30.67,
        "duration": 3.4
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m fine thank you, and you?",
        "start": 34.07,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "Hi, how are you?",
        "start": 37.51,
        "duration": 2.63
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m fine thank you, and you?",
        "start": 40.14,
        "duration": 3.189
    },
    {
        "text": "Hi, how are you?",
        "start": 43.329,
        "duration": 3.431
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m fine thank you, and you?",
        "start": 46.76,
        "duration": 2.93
    },
    {
        "text": "Hi, how are you?",
        "start": 49.69,
        "duration": 3.61
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m fine thank you, and you?",
        "start": 53.3,
        "duration": 4.64
    },
    {
        "text": "I think you get the idea.",
        "start": 57.94,
        "duration": 4.31
    },
    {
        "text": "Even with very simple language, it’s better\nif your language is varied.",
        "start": 62.25,
        "duration": 5.47
    },
    {
        "text": "So, how can you make this more interesting?",
        "start": 67.72,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Here are a few ideas.",
        "start": 72.72,
        "duration": 5.78
    },
    {
        "text": "Hi, how are you?",
        "start": 78.5,
        "duration": 2.06
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m good, thanks, you?",
        "start": 80.57,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "Hi, how are you?",
        "start": 83.45,
        "duration": 2.49
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m pretty good.",
        "start": 85.94,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Hi, how are you?",
        "start": 88.1,
        "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m OK.",
        "start": 90.94,
        "duration": 1.57
    },
    {
        "text": "Hi, how are you?",
        "start": 92.51,
        "duration": 2.74
    },
    {
        "text": "Not bad, thanks.",
        "start": 95.25,
        "duration": 2.52
    },
    {
        "text": "Hi, how are you?",
        "start": 97.77,
        "duration": 2.61
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m very well.",
        "start": 100.38,
        "duration": 2.98
    },
    {
        "text": "Hi, how are you?",
        "start": 103.36,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m great!",
        "start": 106.8,
        "duration": 3.1
    },
    {
        "text": "Remember that it’s polite to also ask the\nother person how they are, too.",
        "start": 109.9,
        "duration": 5.31
    },
    {
        "text": "You can do this by simply adding you?",
        "start": 115.21,
        "duration": 2.86
    },
    {
        "text": "Or, and you?",
        "start": 118.07,
        "duration": 2.36
    },
    {
        "text": "For example:",
        "start": 120.43,
        "duration": 1.94
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m very well, and you?",
        "start": 122.37,
        "duration": 4.71
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m great!",
        "start": 127.08,
        "duration": 0.96
    },
    {
        "text": "You?",
        "start": 128.04,
        "duration": 1.96
    },
    {
        "text": "Notice that the intonation rises at the end\nto show that you’re asking a question.",
        "start": 130.0,
        "duration": 5.59
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, you’ve learned some ways to answer\nthe question how are you, but what about the",
        "start": 135.59,
        "duration": 6.5
    },
    {
        "text": "question itself?",
        "start": 142.09,
        "duration": 1.79
    },
    {
        "text": "Like I’m fine, there are many ways to ask\nhow are you, and you should try to add variety",
        "start": 147.66,
        "duration": 7.25
    },
    {
        "text": "to your English when you speak.",
        "start": 154.91,
        "duration": 3.63
    },
    {
        "text": "By the way, you probably wouldn’t ask a\nperson you see regularly ‘how are you?’.",
        "start": 158.54,
        "duration": 7.72
    },
    {
        "text": "If you see them often it might sound strange\nbecause nothing has changed since the last",
        "start": 166.26,
        "duration": 6.85
    },
    {
        "text": "time you saw them.",
        "start": 173.11,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "Here are a few alternatives you can use.",
        "start": 175.54,
        "duration": 3.74
    },
    {
        "text": "These are more informal, but they’re very\ncommon in everyday situations.",
        "start": 179.28,
        "duration": 4.94
    },
    {
        "text": "How’s it going?",
        "start": 184.22,
        "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
        "text": "How’re things?",
        "start": 186.4,
        "duration": 1.94
    },
    {
        "text": "How’re you doing?",
        "start": 188.34,
        "duration": 2.93
    },
    {
        "text": "How’s life?",
        "start": 191.27,
        "duration": 3.38
    },
    {
        "text": "In informal spoken English, you should use\ncontractions and link words to sound natural.",
        "start": 194.65,
        "duration": 7.48
    },
    {
        "text": "So, make sure you say How’s it going, with\na contraction of is.",
        "start": 202.13,
        "duration": 7.939
    },
    {
        "text": "You can’t use the full form—How is it\ngoing—unless you want to sound like a robot.",
        "start": 210.069,
        "duration": 6.661
    },
    {
        "text": "Similarly, how’re you doing needs to be\npronounced with a contraction of are: how’re",
        "start": 216.73,
        "duration": 6.51
    },
    {
        "text": "you doing?",
        "start": 223.24,
        "duration": 2.54
    },
    {
        "text": "You can even leave out the word are and just\nsay how you doing?",
        "start": 225.78,
        "duration": 5.2
    },
    {
        "text": "Next, let’s see how you can put these greetings\ntogether in a real situation.",
        "start": 230.98,
        "duration": 6.48
    },
    {
        "text": "Hey!",
        "start": 237.46,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "How’s it going?",
        "start": 238.46,
        "duration": 2.2
    },
    {
        "text": "Pretty good thanks, you?",
        "start": 240.66,
        "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah, not bad.",
        "start": 242.84,
        "duration": 1.83
    },
    {
        "text": "Hi, Olivier, how’re things?",
        "start": 244.67,
        "duration": 4.24
    },
    {
        "text": "Good, thanks, and you?",
        "start": 248.91,
        "duration": 3.21
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m good!",
        "start": 252.12,
        "duration": 1.99
    },
    {
        "text": "Next, let’s look at some even more informal\nways of asking or answering the question how",
        "start": 254.11,
        "duration": 7.58
    },
    {
        "text": "are you.",
        "start": 261.69,
        "duration": 0.91
    },
    {
        "text": "Here are three very informal questions you\ncan use to ask how are you:",
        "start": 266.76,
        "duration": 7.18
    },
    {
        "text": "How’s tricks?",
        "start": 273.95,
        "duration": 3.24
    },
    {
        "text": "What’s up?",
        "start": 277.19,
        "duration": 1.69
    },
    {
        "text": "What’s new?",
        "start": 278.88,
        "duration": 2.36
    },
    {
        "text": "Alright?",
        "start": 281.24,
        "duration": 4.04
    },
    {
        "text": "Remember that these are very informal.",
        "start": 285.28,
        "duration": 3.38
    },
    {
        "text": "That doesn’t mean they’re rude or that\nyou shouldn’t use them, but you can’t",
        "start": 288.66,
        "duration": 4.91
    },
    {
        "text": "use them in more formal situations.",
        "start": 293.57,
        "duration": 4.31
    },
    {
        "text": "And yes, how’s tricks is grammatically incorrect,\nbut that’s the phrase which people use!",
        "start": 297.88,
        "duration": 7.87
    },
    {
        "text": "These are common between friends and people\nwho know each other well.",
        "start": 305.75,
        "duration": 4.97
    },
    {
        "text": "Remember what you learned about linking words\nearlier?",
        "start": 310.72,
        "duration": 3.35
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s also important here.",
        "start": 314.07,
        "duration": 3.13
    },
    {
        "text": "You don’t say, What is up?",
        "start": 317.2,
        "duration": 3.02
    },
    {
        "text": "You say, What’s up?",
        "start": 320.22,
        "duration": 2.74
    },
    {
        "text": "And, you don’t say, What is new?",
        "start": 322.96,
        "duration": 2.95
    },
    {
        "text": "You say, What’s new?",
        "start": 325.91,
        "duration": 5.06
    },
    {
        "text": "These different questions can also have different\nresponses.",
        "start": 330.97,
        "duration": 3.02
    },
    {
        "text": "Let’s look!",
        "start": 333.99,
        "duration": 3.39
    },
    {
        "text": "Alright?",
        "start": 337.38,
        "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah, you?",
        "start": 338.4,
        "duration": 2.3
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah, not bad.",
        "start": 340.7,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "What’s new?",
        "start": 344.38,
        "duration": 1.56
    },
    {
        "text": "Not a lot!",
        "start": 345.94,
        "duration": 1.18
    },
    {
        "text": "You?",
        "start": 347.12,
        "duration": 2.269
    },
    {
        "text": "Nothing much.",
        "start": 349.389,
        "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
        "text": "It might sound negative to you to just say\nnothing, but it’s a very common expression",
        "start": 352.389,
        "duration": 6.091
    },
    {
        "text": "to say that you’re well.",
        "start": 358.48,
        "duration": 3.14
    },
    {
        "text": "Because these are very informal ways to ask\nhow are you, sometimes they’re used as greetings.",
        "start": 361.62,
        "duration": 7.47
    },
    {
        "text": "This means that sometimes these questions\ndon’t need an answer.",
        "start": 369.09,
        "duration": 4.829
    },
    {
        "text": "When using these phrases, you can simply answer\nwith an informal greeting, like this:",
        "start": 373.919,
        "duration": 6.381
    },
    {
        "text": "What’s up?",
        "start": 380.3,
        "duration": 2.52
    },
    {
        "text": "Hey, what’s up?",
        "start": 382.82,
        "duration": 2.3
    },
    {
        "text": "Alright?",
        "start": 385.12,
        "duration": 1.62
    },
    {
        "text": "Hey!",
        "start": 386.74,
        "duration": 2.399
    },
    {
        "text": "What else do you need to think about in these\nsituations?",
        "start": 389.139,
        "duration": 3.381
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s important that you continue the conversation\nafter you answer the how are you question.",
        "start": 392.52,
        "duration": 8.17
    },
    {
        "text": "How can you do that?",
        "start": 400.69,
        "duration": 4.47
    },
    {
        "text": "Even if you’re a master of greeting phrases\nin English, that won’t help you if this happens:",
        "start": 405.16,
        "duration": 6.98
    },
    {
        "text": "Hi, how are you?",
        "start": 412.14,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m fine thank you, and you?",
        "start": 413.88,
        "duration": 5.19
    },
    {
        "text": "Fine thanks.",
        "start": 419.07,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "So, what can you say after the initial greeting?",
        "start": 421.87,
        "duration": 9.13
    },
    {
        "text": "You have many choices!",
        "start": 431.0,
        "duration": 1.97
    },
    {
        "text": "Basically, you can make a statement, or ask\na question.",
        "start": 432.97,
        "duration": 4.83
    },
    {
        "text": "For example, you could tell the other person\nsomething about yourself and your life, like",
        "start": 437.8,
        "duration": 7.151
    },
    {
        "text": "this:",
        "start": 444.951,
        "duration": 1.808
    },
    {
        "text": "Actually, work was pretty stressful, but now\nI’m looking forward to…",
        "start": 446.76,
        "duration": 9.54
    },
    {
        "text": "I had a really good day today, because…",
        "start": 456.3,
        "duration": 5.56
    },
    {
        "text": "I’ve just been to…",
        "start": 461.86,
        "duration": 4.9
    },
    {
        "text": "Or there’s always the weather!",
        "start": 466.77,
        "duration": 2.01
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s really hot today, isn’t it?",
        "start": 468.78,
        "duration": 3.4
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s been so wet the last few days.",
        "start": 472.18,
        "duration": 3.609
    },
    {
        "text": "Hopefully it’ll be brighter this weekend!",
        "start": 475.789,
        "duration": 3.38
    },
    {
        "text": "British people love to talk about the weather,\nif you hadn’t realised yet!",
        "start": 479.169,
        "duration": 5.411
    },
    {
        "text": "You can also ask another question, such as:",
        "start": 484.58,
        "duration": 5.209
    },
    {
        "text": "How was your day?",
        "start": 489.789,
        "duration": 1.641
    },
    {
        "text": "How’s your day going?",
        "start": 491.43,
        "duration": 4.519
    },
    {
        "text": "How was your weekend?",
        "start": 495.949,
        "duration": 3.451
    },
    {
        "text": "If you’re even more confident, or you know more\nabout the person you’re talking to, you",
        "start": 499.4,
        "duration": 5.06
    },
    {
        "text": "can go into more detail and ask them more\nspecific questions.",
        "start": 504.46,
        "duration": 4.61
    },
    {
        "text": "For example:",
        "start": 509.07,
        "duration": 1.96
    },
    {
        "text": "How was your trip to Madrid last weekend?",
        "start": 511.03,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "Did you watch the football last night?",
        "start": 514.55,
        "duration": 2.489
    },
    {
        "text": "Is your brother visiting you next week, or\nis it the week after?",
        "start": 517.039,
        "duration": 4.571
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, you should know how to greet people,\nhow to ask and answer how are you in different",
        "start": 521.61,
        "duration": 6.75
    },
    {
        "text": "ways, and how to continue the conversation.",
        "start": 528.36,
        "duration": 4.319
    },
    {
        "text": "Let’s see how you can put everything together.",
        "start": 532.68,
        "duration": 3.46
    },
    {
        "text": "Hey, how are things?",
        "start": 539.86,
        "duration": 1.979
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m good thanks, but a little tired today:\nbusy at work.",
        "start": 541.839,
        "duration": 6.73
    },
    {
        "text": "How about you?",
        "start": 548.569,
        "duration": 2.131
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m well, but I’ve got a lot at work too.",
        "start": 550.7,
        "duration": 3.86
    },
    {
        "text": "How was your trip to Madrid last weekend?",
        "start": 554.56,
        "duration": 2.009
    },
    {
        "text": "Fantastic!",
        "start": 556.569,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s a really great city.",
        "start": 557.569,
        "duration": 3.58
    },
    {
        "text": "What did you do last weekend?",
        "start": 561.149,
        "duration": 3.341
    },
    {
        "text": "Nothing much, just relaxed on the beach!",
        "start": 564.49,
        "duration": 4.469
    },
    {
        "text": "Very nice!",
        "start": 568.96,
        "duration": 1.96
    },
    {
        "text": "Hi, what’s new?",
        "start": 570.92,
        "duration": 2.62
    },
    {
        "text": "Not much, you?",
        "start": 573.54,
        "duration": 2.39
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah, alright.",
        "start": 575.93,
        "duration": 2.29
    },
    {
        "text": "You look a bit tired.",
        "start": 578.22,
        "duration": 2.26
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah, I didn’t sleep well last night.",
        "start": 580.48,
        "duration": 3.9
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh no, why not?",
        "start": 584.38,
        "duration": 3.319
    },
    {
        "text": "My neighbours had a big party and it was really\nloud.",
        "start": 587.699,
        "duration": 5.811
    },
    {
        "text": "I hate it when people do that.",
        "start": 593.51,
        "duration": 3.09
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah, me too.",
        "start": 596.6,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "Anyway, how’s your day going?",
        "start": 598.92,
        "duration": 3.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, it’s your turn to practice!",
        "start": 602.08,
        "duration": 3.1
    },
    {
        "text": "Imagine somebody asks how are you?",
        "start": 605.189,
        "duration": 4.39
    },
    {
        "text": "Can you write down five possible things you\ncould say?",
        "start": 609.579,
        "duration": 4.04
    },
    {
        "text": "Pause the video and write down your answers\nnow.",
        "start": 613.62,
        "duration": 6.94
    },
    {
        "text": "Ready?",
        "start": 620.56,
        "duration": 1.52
    },
    {
        "text": "Let’s look.",
        "start": 622.08,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "Of course, there are more than five possible\nanswers.",
        "start": 623.689,
        "duration": 3.791
    },
    {
        "text": "These are just suggestions:",
        "start": 627.48,
        "duration": 2.28
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m good.",
        "start": 629.76,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m pretty good.",
        "start": 631.52,
        "duration": 2.36
    },
    {
        "text": "Not bad.",
        "start": 633.88,
        "duration": 2.58
    },
    {
        "text": "A little bit tired.",
        "start": 636.47,
        "duration": 1.69
    },
    {
        "text": "Great, thanks!",
        "start": 638.16,
        "duration": 2.219
    },
    {
        "text": "And what about different ways to ask how are\nyou?",
        "start": 640.379,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "What can you say?",
        "start": 644.059,
        "duration": 2.881
    },
    {
        "text": "Pause the video and write down five different\nways to ask this question.",
        "start": 646.94,
        "duration": 5.509
    },
    {
        "text": "OK?",
        "start": 652.449,
        "duration": 1.971
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, these are just suggestions.",
        "start": 654.42,
        "duration": 3.38
    },
    {
        "text": "There are many possibilities!",
        "start": 657.8,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "How’s it going?",
        "start": 660.56,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "How’re you doing?",
        "start": 662.23,
        "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
        "text": "What’s up?",
        "start": 664.41,
        "duration": 2.359
    },
    {
        "text": "How’s life?",
        "start": 666.769,
        "duration": 2.37
    },
    {
        "text": "How’re things?",
        "start": 669.139,
        "duration": 2.37
    },
    {
        "text": "And what do you do next?",
        "start": 671.509,
        "duration": 1.781
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you stop talking?",
        "start": 673.29,
        "duration": 1.32
    },
    {
        "text": "No; keep going!",
        "start": 674.61,
        "duration": 2.069
    },
    {
        "text": "Ask a question or make a statement to continue\nthe conversation.",
        "start": 676.679,
        "duration": 5.871
    },
    {
        "text": "Remember that you can find more great free\nEnglish lessons like this on our website:",
        "start": 682.55,
        "duration": 5.949
    },
    {
        "text": "Oxford Online English dot com.",
        "start": 688.499,
        "duration": 3.171
    },
    {
        "text": "Thanks for watching!",
        "start": 691.67,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
